HCI Term Project Idea
Theme: Campus safety

Motos:
Help us help you!

Android App with following features:

Panic
- allow to send campus security GPS location for emergency use also calls campus security

Report 
- allow to send report to campus security about an issue

News feed 
- provides information to user on live reports or recent incidents

Map with user input 
- allow user to select area on map and place comment
- user can highlight some hazard, construction, congestion, spills, damage, etc
- will be highlighted for all users on their news feed and on the campus map within the app
- implement learning algorithm to find most common place of hazards (pair with time?, frequency?, location?)
